<div class="j7-panel-content j7-layout-manager">
  <header class="j7-panel-head">
    <div class="j7-flex-row j7-flex-between j7-flex-center">
      <div>
        <h3><i class="fas fa-up-down-left-right"></i> Layout & Modul Manager</h3>
        <p class="muted">Verwalte welche Module auf welcher Oberfläche erscheinen sollen.</p>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="j7-shell__btn" data-action="resetAllLayouts">
        <i class="fas fa-trash-can"></i> Alle zurücksetzen
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="j7-layout-grid">
    <table class="janus7-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 40px;"></th>
          <th>Modul</th>
          <th>Sichtbarkeit (Oberflächen)</th>
          <th style="width: 80px; text-align: center;">Aktiv</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each modules}}
          <tr class="j7-module-row {{#unless isActive}}is-disabled{{/unless}}">
            <td><i class="{{icon}} j7-text-info"></i></td>
            <td>
              <div class="j7-flex-column">
                <strong>{{title}}</strong>
                <span class="small muted">{{description}}</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>
              <div class="j7-multi-select-surface">
                {{#each ../views}}
                  <label class="j7-surface-chip {{#if (includedIn ../assignedTo id)}}is-assigned{{/if}}" 
                         data-action="toggleModuleAssignment" 
                         data-module-id="{{../id}}" 
                         data-view-id="{{id}}"
                         title="{{title}}">
                    <i class="{{icon}}"></i>
                    <span>{{title}}</span>
                  </label>
                {{/each}}
              </div>
            </td>
            <td style="text-align: center;">
              <input type="checkbox" 
                     class="janus7-checkbox" 
                     data-action="toggleModuleGlobal" 
                     data-module-id="{{id}}" 
                     {{#if isActive}}checked{{/if}} />
            </td>
          </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <footer class="j7-panel-footer j7-mt-md">
    <div class="j7-callout j7-callout--info">
      <i class="fas fa-circle-info"></i>
      <p>Änderungen werden sofort gespeichert und wirken sich auf die jeweiligen Ansichten aus. Aktiviere den <strong>Layout-Editor</strong> in der jeweiligen Ansicht, um die Positionen innerhalb des Rasters anzupassen.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>

<style>
.j7-multi-select-surface {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 4px;
}

.j7-surface-chip {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  user-select: none;
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.j7-surface-chip:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  opacity: 1;
}

.j7-surface-chip.is-assigned {
  background: var(--j7-color-info-muted);
  border-color: var(--j7-color-info);
  color: var(--j7-color-info);
  opacity: 1;
}

.j7-module-row.is-disabled {
  opacity: 0.4;
  filter: grayscale(0.8);
}
</style>
